<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Account Deleted</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #343a40; color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Account Deleted</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>This email confirms that your <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> account and all associated data have been permanently deleted on {{deletionDate}}.</p>

    {{#if isTrialExpired}}
    <p>Your account was deleted because your free trial ended without an active subscription.</p>
    {{else if isImmediateDeletion}}
    <p>Your account was deleted at your request. We're sorry to see you go!</p>
    {{else}}
    <p>Your account was deleted following your subscription cancellation and the 30-day data retention period.</p>
    {{/if}}

    <div style="background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>What was deleted:</strong></p>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>All photographs and uploaded files</li>
        <li>All rolls, collections, and galleries</li>
        <li>Person profiles and contact information</li>
        <li>Moodboards and contact sheets</li>
        <li>Account settings and preferences</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Want to start fresh?</strong></p>
    <p>You're always welcome to create a new account and start a new free trial at any time.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{baseUrl}}/signup" style="background-color: #28a745; color: #fff; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
        Start New Trial
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
      Thank you for trying Only35. We hope to see you again in the future!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>This is an automated message from Only35.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
